Property.name: Angle
Property.doc: The rotation angle of the second plane about its z-axis. You need to enable LockAngle for this to take effect.

Property.name: AnglePitch
Property.doc: Rotation angle of the second plane about its y-axis. You need to enable LockAngle for this to take effect.

Property.name: AngleRoll
Property.doc: Rotation angle of the second plane about its x-axis You need to enable LockAngle for this to take effect.

Property.name: LockAngle
Property.doc: Enforce an angle offset defined as yaw-pitch-roll angle of the second plane performed in the order of x-y-z
